OL,3,C'Momentum growing' in UK plum industry
OL,4,Cwith bumper crop, says grower
OL,6,FThe UK plum industry has begun to pull
OL,7,Fout of a "decades-long decline" with a
OL,8,Fbumper crop reported this year, a
OL,9,Fgrower has said.
OL,11,FPlum production in the UK hit its peak
OL,12,Fin 1987 with 28,900 tonnes being
OL,13,Fproduced that year, according to Defra
OL,14,Ffigures.
OL,16,FDue to lower yields and cheaper
OL,17,Fimports, the industry then declined,
OL,18,Fhitting its lowest point in 2008 with
OL,19,Ftotal production of just 2,500 tonnes.
