OL,3,C'Momentum growing' in UK plum industry
OL,4,Cwith bumper crop, says grower
OL,6,FSince then, growers have adjusted to
OL,7,Ffinding new plum varieties and modern
OL,8,Ffarming systems, and the production
OL,9,Fthis summer is set to be the biggest
OL,10,Fin three years, according to fruit
OL,11,Fgrower WB Chambers, based in
OL,12,FMaidstone, Kent.
OL,14,FIts commercial director James Miller
OL,15,Fsaid: "The UK plum industry has now
OL,16,Fstarted to pull out of a decades-long
OL,17,Fdecline and the quality of the fruit
OL,18,Fcoming through right now, and the
OL,19,Fyield, is the best we've seen for ages.
