OL,3,C'Momentum growing' in UK plum industry
OL,4,Cwith bumper crop, says grower
OL,6,F"There is a real momentum growing
OL,7,Fwithin the plum industry again."
OL,9,FThe UK's plum production area fell
OL,10,Ffrom 2,400 hectares in 1985 to 800
OL,11,Fhectares in 2017 as growers turned to
OL,12,Ffruits with higher profitability.
OL,14,FMr Miller added: "As cheaper imports
OL,15,Fflooded the market and plum production
OL,16,Fbecame less profitable, interest in
OL,17,Fgrowing the fruit dwindled.
