OL,3,C'Momentum growing' in UK plum industry
OL,4,Cwith bumper crop, says grower
OL,6,F"But we have now invested in new root
OL,7,Fstocks as well as modern farming
OL,8,Fsystems such as automatic minimal
OL,9,Firrigation and soil moisture analysis."
OL,11,FWB Chambers said the new varieties as
OL,12,Fwell as this year's perfect growing
OL,13,Fconditions means it has doubled its
OL,14,Fproduction from 150 tonnes in 2024 to
OL,15,F300 tonnes this summer.
