OL,3,C'Momentum growing' in UK plum industry
OL,4,Cwith bumper crop, says grower
OL,6,FTesco fruit category buying manager
OL,7,FSimon Reeves said: "We are hearing
OL,8,Fsimilar reports from all our growers
OL,9,Fand main plum supplier that this has
OL,10,Fbeen the best harvest for about three
OL,11,Fyears.
OL,13,F"The quality of the British-grown
OL,14,Fplums arriving at our stores across
OL,15,Fthe UK right now is easily the best
OL,16,Fwe've seen for several years ` plump,
OL,17,Fjuicy and sweet."
OL,19,FThe grower also said new varieties of
OL,20,Fplum have a better shelf life that
OL,21,Fwill help cut down on wastage.
